These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: epic, musical
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, swisher
1. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | epic  | musical |
| Cigar     | swisher | oliveros  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: white, pink
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skateboarding, snowboarding
1. the person who likes pink is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Color    | white      | pink         |
| Sport   | skateboarding | snowboarding |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, soy-milk
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, dannemann
1. the person drinking milk is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | milk   |
| Cigar       | dannemann  | montecristo |

 #################################

 
